# Fail closed: the Dockerfile may receive only the exact public inputs it copies.
*
!.dockerignore
!Dockerfile
!pyproject.toml
!README.md
!LICENSE
!NOTICE
!requirements/
!requirements/runtime.txt
!.clusterfuzzlite/
!.clusterfuzzlite/**
!fuzz/
!fuzz/**
!src/
!src/**
!examples/
