# never be reintroduced into the build context.
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/.internal
**/.internal/**
**/.codex
**/.codex/**
**/.claude
**/.claude/**
**/private-traces
**/private-traces/**
**/raw-model-responses
**/raw-model-responses/**
**/attack-vectors
**/attack-vectors/**
**/canary-runs
**/canary-runs/**
**/reports
**/reports/**
**/*.db
**/*.sqlite3
**/__pycache__
**/__pycache__/**
**/*.pyc
